---
import Bi from '../shared/Bi.astro';
import Callout from '../shared/Callout.astro';
import Section from '../mechanics/Section.astro';
---
<Section id="task-bonuses" titleZh="任務獎勵：新手免費資源" titleEn="Task rewards: free starter resources" eyebrow="Day 0–14">
  <p>
    <Bi
      zh="開新帳號會出現任務系統（Adviser quests），每完成一個給資源 / 銀幣 / 物品。Lumi 強調「Spawn village 拿全部 task bonus」是早期最高 ROI 之一，因為相對於建造成本，獎勵超大。"
      en="New accounts get an Adviser quest system; each completed task rewards resources / silver / items. Lumi emphasizes 'grab every task bonus on spawn village' as one of the highest-ROI activities early game — rewards are huge relative to the actions required."
    />
  </p>

  <h3><Bi zh="任務類型" en="Quest categories" /></h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong><Bi zh="Adviser 任務" en="Adviser quests" /></strong>: <Bi zh="教學引導，依序完成（蓋第一個建築 / 第一次掠奪 / 升 MB Lv 5 等）。每階段獎勵約 100–500 資源 + 偶爾銀幣或冒險點" en="Tutorial flow, sequential (build first building / first raid / MB Lv 5 etc.). Each rewards ~100–500 resources + occasional silver or adventure points" /></li>
    <li><strong><Bi zh="Daily 任務" en="Daily quests" /></strong>: <Bi zh="每天刷新，做特定動作換獎勵點數" en="Refresh daily, complete specific actions for reward points" /></li>
    <li><strong><Bi zh="World 任務" en="World quests" /></strong>: <Bi zh="長期目標（達 X 人口、佔領 Y 個綠洲），獎勵更大" en="Long-term goals (reach X population, capture Y oases), bigger rewards" /></li>
    <li><strong><Bi zh="Beginner Protection 期間額外獎勵" en="Beginner-protection bonus rewards" /></strong>: <Bi zh="保護期內完成任務有額外資源加成" en="Extra resource bonus on tasks completed during protection" /></li>
  </ul>

  <Callout kind="tip" titleZh="優先做哪些 task" titleEn="Which tasks to prioritize">
    <p>
      <Bi
        zh="優先：(1) 一次性的「建造 X / 訓練 Y」任務，不做白不做；(2) 把 spawn 城所有 adviser 任務全跑完，獎勵總和約 5–10k 資源 + 幾百銀幣；(3) Daily quest 集滿換『金幣寶箱』長期值。Skip：太繞路或要花真金的「達 X 人口」之類晚期任務。"
        en="Prioritize: (1) one-shot 'build X / train Y' tasks — free completions; (2) finish ALL adviser tasks on spawn (~5–10k total resources + a few hundred silver); (3) daily quests for the gold-chest long-term grind. Skip: late-game pop-target quests that distract from real planning."
      />
    </p>
  </Callout>

  <p style="font-size: var(--fs-sm); color: var(--text-2);">
    <Bi
      zh="任務獎勵可以等到當下需要時才領（按下 Adviser → Reward 領取）。Lumi 建議：要訓開拓者前一刻才領，因為剛好把成本補回來。"
      en="Rewards can be claimed on demand (Adviser → Reward). Lumi tip: hold off claiming until just before training Settlers — the rewards conveniently offset Settler cost."
    />
  </p>
</Section>
